  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-weaponproperties.HU4lNUAme2XmxfAN]{Weapon Group: Small Arms, One-Handed}&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">This pistol-shaped weapon from Mann launches a balloon-like force field, capturing a target by warping its containment matrix around its victim and then compressing the field to restrain the target from moving. If this weapon strikes a target, it is @Compendium[combat-utility-belt.conditionsdnd5e.0mkU8eksNfwd1AZY]{Restrained}: the victim needs to make a DC15 Dexterity or Dexterity</span>&nbsp; <span class=\"fontstyle0\">(Acrobatics) check to escape. Only Large targets or smaller can be targeted. A target can be hit additional times, each time increasing the save DC by +2 (maximum DC25).</span></p>\n<table class=\"NormalTable\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 90px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Restrainment field </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 38px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">2,800 </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 46px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Special </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 52px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">50/200 </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 46px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">5 lb. </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 112px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Reload (4-H), TL4</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-weaponproperties.QjoW3JNAsq3eJt4s]{Reload 4-H} @Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-equipment.JKcEAJ4xm2Us5hYN]{Battry Cell, High}</p>",
